📚 Additions
* The Radar Screen now shows info about neighboring sectors including name, callsign, frequency and a heading towards the sector.
* Added relevant waypoints to the radar screen for all major airports
* Aircraft wake categories (if included in callsign) will now be replaced with their identifier
e.g. "Heavy" -> /H, "Super" -> /J

Happy Controlling
